Below are several groups you can support. They are on the frontlines providing emergency medical care, supplies, food, shelter, etc. You can find links to each of these organizations in my stories & highlights. 

Magen David Adom - Israel’s national emergency medical service on the frontlines of saving lives in Israel 
@mdaisrael.en @magen_david_adom_america 

American Friends of Combatants For Peace  - Combatants for Peace (CfP) is a grassroots movement of Palestinians and Israelis, working together to end the occupation and bring sustainable peace, equality, and freedom to our homeland.
@combatants4peace @combatantsforpeace 

Round Up - Raising funds for carefully vetted organizations ensuring that Israeli families left homeless have food, clothing and hygiene products.

Palestine Children's Relief Fund (PCRF) - Providing urgent humanitarian care for Gaza's children amidst the unfolding crisis in Gaza. 
@thepcrf 

~Erin xo

